main event: Observers sighted a traveling contrail moving WSW at an estimated speed of 1400 mph in Guam.
interesting points: The contrail dissipated almost immediately after formation.,The color of the contrail was described as white.,The object was sighted by military observers from an aircraft.,The estimated altitude of the contrail was between 30,000 and 35,000 feet.,The sighting lasted for approximately one minute.
